# Changelog

::: {#52f81cca .cell execution_count=1}
``` {.python .cell-code}
import pyfixest as pf
from pyfixest.report.utils import rename_categoricals

df = pf.get_data()

fit1 = pf.feols("Y ~ X1", data = df)
fit2 = pf.feols("Y ~ X1 + X2", data = df)
fit3 = pf.feols("Y ~ X1 + X2 | f1", data = df)
```

