## PyFixest 0.21.0

- Add support for randomization inference via the `ritest()` method:

::: {#67232320 .cell execution_count=20}
``` {.python .cell-code}
import pyfixest as pf
data = pf.get_data()

fit = pf.feols("Y ~ X1", data = data)
fit.ritest(resampvar="X1=0", reps = 1000)
```
:::


